		</figure>
		<p>The journey towards Redpoint V1 started with a prototype code named Newton. We knew that we wanted to begin automating a lot of our existing integration services, but we didn't know what exactly that should look like. Over the course of a few weeks I put together a prototype with a hodgepodge of ideas and features. Below you'll find a series screenshots of the prototype showing various views. Note - this was built using Angular JS and a custom Sass framework I developed in house at Catalyze.</p>
