		<p>Since selling to healthcare institutions can often be a complex three headed beast the core purpose of this early prototype was to gain valuable insight about it's utility from potential buyers. Once we had validated our idea of the product in the marketplace we'd then design a new experience around real users. These prototypes included two core features that we knew were vital to our success. Those include the ability to create an interface and to view metrics about interface usage.</p>
